description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Beginner Flow' from the channel Owen Henn.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow vibe.
The The Zen Flow vibe means Grounding, intentional, breath-centered, unhurried. This is especially good for When you need balance, mindfulness, and release..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Build heat throughout your body with Owen and Aisyah in this yoga flow for all levels. ...
